
  Applin    Grass Type Pokémon

  It spends its entire life inside 
  an apple.  It hides from its 
  natural enemies, bird Pokémon, 
  by pretending it’s just an apple 
  and nothing more. 
	Evolution Chain
      Applin ► Flapple

Stage 2 Forms:
  flapple
  appletun

